er 8 missions to go through). I was stunned, but sad, because I loved to look out for every new planet to get new stuff. And now I have everything and the fun to play the game and achieve more things really stopped, I don't even want to play the game anymore, the story mode was all that kept me here (because of the problems above).PS: It does show, that the game has 32 achievements. But neither can i see them nor did i laready got one. Is it blocked because of the Early Access? Or do I have another issue (I use the german steam layout)."
